          "process_md": "\n1. Applicants should contact to their nearest [District Program Officer (DPO).](https://sswcd.punjab.gov.in/en/contact-us/district-program-officer)1. Application Form will be provided by the Concerned DPO.\n1. Fill up the aplication form and submit all the required documents.\n1. Verification of the applicant will be done by the concerned authority.\n1. After verification eligible applicant can avail the benefit of the Scheme.\n\n<br>\n\n"
